gov.ca.dsm2.input.model
Class Reservoir

java.lang.Object
  gov.ca.dsm2.input.model.Reservoir
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Reservoir
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Represents a reservoir in the model DSM2Model and contained by Reservoirs. Its identified by a name getName() and defined by an area getArea(), a bottom elevation getBottomElevation() and its connections getReservoirConnections()

GIS information is represented by the general location getLatitude() and getLongitude() and its outline by getLatLngPoints()
